---
title: All Tags
---

- content_for :meta_desc do
  = tag "meta", name: "description", content: "All Tags"

%section.container.navbar-top-spacing.container--spacing
  .column
    .tag-view__title.container--title-area
      %h1 All Tags

    %ul.tag-list
      - blog.tags.sort.each do |tag, articles|
        %li.tag-list__item= link_to "#{tag} (#{articles.size})", tag_path(tag)
